                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirement</strong> The poltergeist must be invisible. <strong>Effect</strong> The poltergeist becomes visible, appearing as a skeletal, ghostlike humanoid. Each creature within 30 feet must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"33\" data-pf2-traits=\"concentrate,emotion,fear,incapacitation,mental\" data-pf2-label=\"Frighten DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save, becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened} 2 on a failure. On a critical failure, it's also @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fleeing]{Fleeing} for as long as it's @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened}. On a success, the creature is temporarily immune for 1 minute. At the start of its next turn, the poltergeist becomes invisible again.</p>"
